IN RE: Brian L. MCCULLOUGH NO. 2019-B-0169 Supreme Court of Louisiana. February 11, 2019

ORDER

Considering the Joint Petition for Interim Suspension filed by respondent, Brian L. McCullough, and the Office of Disciplinary Counsel,

IT IS ORDERED that Brian L. McCullough, Louisiana Bar Roll number 31256, be and he hereby is suspended from the practice of law on an interim basis pursuant to Supreme Court Rule XIX, § 19.3, pending further orders of this court. Pursuant to Supreme Court Rule XIX, § 26(E), this order is effective immediately.
